	<entry>
		<title>Catharsis</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/4-catharsis"/>
		<published>2015-04-19T18:59:33+00:00</published>
		<updated>2015-04-19T18:59:33+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/4-catharsis</id>
		<author>
			<name>Kate Coady</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/116-nigel-brown&quot;&gt;Nigel Brown&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/4-catharsis&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/piranesi-arch-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A black-and-white line drawing of stairways and confusing architecture.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;&quot;After a hundred thousand years, it was time to clear out these Levels of the Long Siege?—?the lowest half-mile of the Pyramid that had borne the greatest brunt of attacks from the Night Land.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/116-nigel-brown&quot;&gt;Nigel Brown&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/4-catharsis&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/piranesi-arch-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A black-and-white line drawing of stairways and confusing architecture.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;&quot;After a hundred thousand years, it was time to clear out these Levels of the Long Siege?—?the lowest half-mile of the Pyramid that had borne the greatest brunt of attacks from the Night Land.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
